quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif-lam-ra tilka ayatualkitabi waqur-anin mubeen"
  15,2,"Rubama yawaddu allatheenakafaroo law kanoo muslimeen"
  15,3,"Tharhum ya/kuloo wayatamattaAAoowayulhihimu al-amalu fasawfa yaAAlamoon"
  15,4,"Wama ahlakna min qaryatin illawalaha kitabun maAAloom"
  15,5,"Ma tasbiqu min ommatin ajalahawama yasta/khiroon"
  15,6,"Waqaloo ya ayyuha allatheenuzzila AAalayhi aththikru innaka lamajnoon"
  15,7,"Law ma ta/teena bilmala-ikatiin kunta mina assadiqeen"
  15,8,"Ma nunazzilu almala-ikata illabilhaqqi wama kanoo ithan munthareen"
  15,9,"Inna nahnu nazzalna aththikrawa-inna lahu lahafithoon"
  15,10,"Walaqad arsalna min qablika feeshiyaAAi al-awwaleen"